{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin","slug":"pip-the-curious-penguin","title":"Pip the Curious Penguin","title_ko":"호기심 많은 펭귄 핍","level":"A2","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/cover.webp","summary_ko":"남극 너머가 궁금했던 펭귄 핍이 용감한 모험을 떠났다가 집과 친구의 소중함을 깨닫고 돌아오는 이야기예요.","wordCount":120,"pages":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Pip was a little penguin with big dreams.","translation_ko":"핍은 큰 꿈을 가진 작은 펭귄이었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":240},{"word":"was","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":240,"endMs":540},{"word":"a","charStart":8,"charEnd":9,"startMs":540,"endMs":760},{"word":"little","charStart":10,"charEnd":16,"startMs":760,"endMs":940},{"word":"penguin","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":940,"endMs":1200},{"word":"with","charStart":25,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1200,"endMs":1620},{"word":"big","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1620,"endMs":1920},{"word":"dreams","charStart":34,"charEnd":40,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2260}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"He always wondered what lay beyond the ice.","translation_ko":"핍은 늘 얼음 너머에 무엇이 있을지 궁금했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"always","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":360,"endMs":1000},{"word":"wondered","charStart":10,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1440},{"word":"what","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1440,"endMs":2020},{"word":"lay","charStart":24,"charEnd":27,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2280},{"word":"beyond","charStart":28,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2700},{"word":"the","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3160},{"word":"ice","charStart":39,"charEnd":42,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3220}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"I want to see the whole world!\" said Pip.","translation_ko":"\"나는 온 세상을 보고 싶어!\" 핍이 말했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"I","charStart":1,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":340},{"word":"want","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":340,"endMs":640},{"word":"to","charStart":8,"charEnd":10,"startMs":640,"endMs":860},{"word":"see","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":860,"endMs":980},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":980,"endMs":1140},{"word":"whole","charStart":19,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1140,"endMs":1500},{"word":"world","charStart":25,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1500,"endMs":2420},{"word":"said","charStart":33,"charEnd":37,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2520},{"word":"Pip","charStart":38,"charEnd":41,"startMs":2520,"endMs":2760}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p2-s2","ord":1,"text":"So one bright morning, he set off.","translation_ko":"그래서 어느 맑은 아침, 핍은 길을 떠났어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p2-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":360},{"word":"one","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":360,"endMs":680},{"word":"bright","charStart":7,"charEnd":13,"startMs":680,"endMs":960},{"word":"morning","charStart":14,"charEnd":21,"startMs":960,"endMs":1260},{"word":"he","charStart":23,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1540},{"word":"set","charStart":26,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1540,"endMs":1760},{"word":"off","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1760,"endMs":2020}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"He slid across the ice and swam through cold waves.","translation_ko":"핍은 얼음 위를 미끄러지고 차가운 파도를 헤엄쳐 갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":300},{"word":"slid","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":300,"endMs":580},{"word":"across","charStart":8,"charEnd":14,"startMs":580,"endMs":900},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":900,"endMs":1400},{"word":"ice","charStart":19,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1400},{"word":"and","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1400,"endMs":2060},{"word":"swam","charStart":27,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2380},{"word":"through","charStart":32,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2700},{"word":"cold","charStart":40,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2700,"endMs":3080},{"word":"waves","charStart":45,"charEnd":50,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3440}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p3-s2","ord":1,"text":"He saw tall mountains and shining stars.","translation_ko":"높은 산들과 반짝이는 별들을 보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p3-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"saw","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":260,"endMs":540},{"word":"tall","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":540,"endMs":940},{"word":"mountains","charStart":12,"charEnd":21,"startMs":940,"endMs":1340},{"word":"and","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1340,"endMs":2140},{"word":"shining","charStart":26,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2140,"endMs":2440},{"word":"stars","charStart":34,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2440,"endMs":2940}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p4","pageNo":4,"spread":"p4","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p4.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p4-s1","ord":0,"text":"But the world was very big and quiet.","translation_ko":"하지만 세상은 아주 크고 고요했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p4-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"the","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":320,"endMs":600},{"word":"world","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":600,"endMs":920},{"word":"was","charStart":14,"charEnd":17,"startMs":920,"endMs":1260},{"word":"very","charStart":18,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1580},{"word":"big","charStart":23,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1900},{"word":"and","charStart":27,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1900,"endMs":2340},{"word":"quiet","charStart":31,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2340,"endMs":2560}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p4-s2","ord":1,"text":"Soon, Pip began to feel lonely.","translation_ko":"이윽고, 핍은 외로워지기 시작했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p4-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Soon","charStart":0,"charEnd":4,"startMs":0,"endMs":700},{"word":"Pip","charStart":6,"charEnd":9,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1080},{"word":"began","charStart":10,"charEnd":15,"startMs":1080,"endMs":1480},{"word":"to","charStart":16,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1940},{"word":"feel","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1940,"endMs":2020},{"word":"lonely","charStart":24,"charEnd":30,"startMs":2020,"endMs":2380}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p5","pageNo":5,"spread":"p5","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p5.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p5-s1","ord":0,"text":"He missed his family and his warm home.","translation_ko":"핍은 가족과 따뜻한 집이 그리웠어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p5-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"missed","charStart":3,"charEnd":9,"startMs":280,"endMs":640},{"word":"his","charStart":10,"charEnd":13,"startMs":640,"endMs":1180},{"word":"family","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1440},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1440,"endMs":2040},{"word":"his","charStart":25,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2380},{"word":"warm","charStart":29,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2640},{"word":"home","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2640,"endMs":2960}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p5-s2","ord":1,"text":"\"Maybe home is the best place,\" he thought.","translation_ko":"\"어쩌면 집이 제일 좋은 곳일지도 몰라.\" 핍은 생각했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p5-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Maybe","charStart":1,"charEnd":6,"startMs":0,"endMs":520},{"word":"home","charStart":7,"charEnd":11,"startMs":520,"endMs":1100},{"word":"is","charStart":12,"charEnd":14,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1280},{"word":"the","charStart":15,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1480},{"word":"best","charStart":19,"charEnd":23,"startMs":1480,"endMs":1740},{"word":"place","charStart":24,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1740,"endMs":2120},{"word":"he","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":2420,"endMs":2580},{"word":"thought","charStart":35,"charEnd":42,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2820}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p6","pageNo":6,"spread":"p6","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p6.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p6-s1","ord":0,"text":"So Pip turned around and traveled back.","translation_ko":"그래서 핍은 돌아서서 집으로 돌아갔어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p6-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"So","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":740},{"word":"Pip","charStart":3,"charEnd":6,"startMs":740,"endMs":1000},{"word":"turned","charStart":7,"charEnd":13,"startMs":1000,"endMs":1340},{"word":"around","charStart":14,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1340,"endMs":1780},{"word":"and","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1780,"endMs":2280},{"word":"traveled","charStart":25,"charEnd":33,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2380},{"word":"back","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2380,"endMs":2820}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p6-s2","ord":1,"text":"His friends were waiting on the ice.","translation_ko":"친구들이 얼음 위에서 기다리고 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p6-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"His","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":260},{"word":"friends","charStart":4,"charEnd":11,"startMs":260,"endMs":700},{"word":"were","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":700,"endMs":960},{"word":"waiting","charStart":17,"charEnd":24,"startMs":960,"endMs":1320},{"word":"on","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1560},{"word":"the","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1560,"endMs":1720},{"word":"ice","charStart":32,"charEnd":35,"startMs":1720,"endMs":1940}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p7","pageNo":7,"spread":"p7","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p7.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p7-s1","ord":0,"text":"\"We missed you, Pip!\" they cheered.","translation_ko":"\"보고 싶었어, 핍!\" 친구들이 환호했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p7-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"We","charStart":1,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"missed","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":320,"endMs":760},{"word":"you","charStart":11,"charEnd":14,"startMs":760,"endMs":1060},{"word":"Pip","charStart":16,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1280,"endMs":1280},{"word":"they","charStart":22,"charEnd":26,"startMs":1740,"endMs":1920},{"word":"cheered","charStart":27,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1920,"endMs":2340}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p7-s2","ord":1,"text":"Pip hugged them with a happy heart.","translation_ko":"핍은 행복한 마음으로 친구들을 안았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p7-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Pip","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":460},{"word":"hugged","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":460,"endMs":860},{"word":"them","charStart":11,"charEnd":15,"startMs":860,"endMs":1020},{"word":"with","charStart":16,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1020,"endMs":1180},{"word":"a","charStart":21,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1180,"endMs":1420},{"word":"happy","charStart":23,"charEnd":28,"startMs":1420,"endMs":1580},{"word":"heart","charStart":29,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1580,"endMs":1880}]}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p8","pageNo":8,"spread":"p8","imageUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/p8.webp","sentences":[{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p8-s1","ord":0,"text":"Now Pip still loves adventures.","translation_ko":"이제도 핍은 여전히 모험을 좋아해요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p8-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Now","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":480},{"word":"Pip","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":480,"endMs":760},{"word":"still","charStart":8,"charEnd":13,"startMs":760,"endMs":1220},{"word":"loves","charStart":14,"charEnd":19,"startMs":1220,"endMs":1640},{"word":"adventures","charStart":20,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1640,"endMs":2120}]},{"id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-p8-s2","ord":1,"text":"But he knows the best one ends at home.","translation_ko":"하지만 가장 멋진 모험은 집에서 끝난다는 걸 알아요.","audioUrl":"/seed/pip-the-curious-penguin/audio/p8-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":320},{"word":"he","charStart":4,"charEnd":6,"startMs":320,"endMs":500},{"word":"knows","charStart":7,"charEnd":12,"startMs":500,"endMs":760},{"word":"the","charStart":13,"charEnd":16,"startMs":760,"endMs":960},{"word":"best","charStart":17,"charEnd":21,"startMs":960,"endMs":1260},{"word":"one","charStart":22,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1600},{"word":"ends","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":1600,"endMs":1880},{"word":"at","charStart":31,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2160},{"word":"home","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2160,"endMs":2420}]}]}],"quiz":[{"question_ko":"핍은 늘 무엇을 궁금해했나요?","type":"mc","options":["누가 더 빠른지","무엇을 먹을지","어떻게 헤엄칠지","얼음 너머에 무엇이 있을지"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"핍은 큰 꿈을 가진 펭귄으로, 늘 얼음 너머의 세상을 궁금해했어요.","id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-q1","ord":0},{"question_ko":"핍은 모험을 떠나 무엇을 보았나요?","type":"mc","options":["사막과 낙타","큰 도시와 자동차","정글과 호랑이","높은 산들과 반짝이는 별들"],"answerIndex":3,"explain_ko":"핍은 얼음을 미끄러지고 파도를 헤엄치며 높은 산과 반짝이는 별을 보았어요.","id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-q2","ord":1},{"question_ko":"넓은 세상에서 핍은 어떤 기분이 들었나요?","type":"mc","options":["외로워졌다","더 신이 났다","화가 났다","졸렸다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"세상은 크고 고요했고, 핍은 가족과 집을 그리워하며 외로워졌어요.","id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-q3","ord":2},{"question_ko":"핍은 결국 어떤 선택을 했나요?","type":"mc","options":["계속 더 멀리 갔다","산에서 살았다","집으로 돌아갔다","새 집을 지었다"],"answerIndex":2,"explain_ko":"\"집이 제일 좋은 곳일지도 몰라\"라고 생각하며 돌아섰어요.","id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-q4","ord":3},{"question_ko":"이 이야기가 주는 교훈은 무엇인가요?","type":"mc","options":["가장 멋진 모험도 집에서 끝난다","혼자가 제일 좋다","꿈은 필요 없다","멀리 갈수록 좋다"],"answerIndex":0,"explain_ko":"핍은 여전히 모험을 좋아하지만, 가장 좋은 모험은 가족이 있는 집으로 돌아오는 것임을 알게 됐어요.","id":"pip-the-curious-penguin-q5","ord":4}]}